responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "4FA593794F8DD9AB1582AFB5E38130D3", "Another newcomer! Hopefully you have recovered from the shock of crossing through the Divine Gateway. We have dire need of new citizens within the Kaelar Empire. If so, then report to Lionhold at once. For greater glory!")
